{"id": 1, "text": "Um, I've had chest pain for three days, mostly on the left side. I take 50 milligrams of Lisinopril every morning and ibuprofen when it gets bad. I had bypass surgery in 2019.", "entities": [{"start": 13, "end": 23, "text": "chest pain", "label": "Symptom"}, {"start": 89, "end": 99, "text": "Lisinopril", "label": "Medication"}, {"start": 118, "end": 127, "text": "ibuprofen", "label": "Medication"}, {"start": 72, "end": 85, "text": "50 milligrams", "label": "Dosage"}, {"start": 152, "end": 166, "text": "bypass surgery", "label": "Medical History"}, {"start": 54, "end": 63, "text": "left side", "label": "Anatomical Site"}, {"start": 28, "end": 38, "text": "three days", "label": "Duration"}, {"start": 100, "end": 113, "text": "every morning", "label": "Frequency"}]}
{"id": 2, "text": "So I feel dizzy and nauseous after lunch, maybe for about two weeks. I'm on Metformin 500mg twice daily, and I had my gallbladder removed years ago.", "entities": [{"start": 10, "end": 15, "text": "dizzy", "label": "Symptom"}, {"start": 20, "end": 28, "text": "nauseous", "label": "Symptom"}, {"start": 76, "end": 85, "text": "Metformin", "label": "Medication"}, {"start": 86, "end": 91, "text": "500mg", "label": "Dosage"}, {"start": 118, "end": 137, "text": "gallbladder removed", "label": "Medical History"}, {"start": 58, "end": 67, "text": "two weeks", "label": "Duration"}, {"start": 92, "end": 103, "text": "twice daily", "label": "Frequency"}]}
{"id": 3, "text": "I've been coughing all night and wheezing in my chest since Monday. I use Albuterol two puffs as needed, and I have asthma from childhood.", "entities": [{"start": 10, "end": 18, "text": "coughing", "label": "Symptom"}, {"start": 33, "end": 41, "text": "wheezing", "label": "Symptom"}, {"start": 74, "end": 83, "text": "Albuterol", "label": "Medication"}, {"start": 84, "end": 93, "text": "two puffs", "label": "Dosage"}, {"start": 116, "end": 122, "text": "asthma", "label": "Medical History"}, {"start": 48, "end": 53, "text": "chest", "label": "Anatomical Site"}, {"start": 54, "end": 66, "text": "since Monday", "label": "Duration"}, {"start": 94, "end": 103, "text": "as needed", "label": "Frequency"}]}
{"id": 4, "text": "My right leg has been swollen for a week, and it hurts when I walk. I take Warfarin 5 mg nightly because I had a blood clot last year.", "entities": [{"start": 22, "end": 29, "text": "swollen", "label": "Symptom"}, {"start": 49, "end": 54, "text": "hurts", "label": "Symptom"}, {"start": 75, "end": 83, "text": "Warfarin", "label": "Medication"}, {"start": 84, "end": 88, "text": "5 mg", "label": "Dosage"}, {"start": 113, "end": 123, "text": "blood clot", "label": "Medical History"}, {"start": 3, "end": 12, "text": "right leg", "label": "Anatomical Site"}, {"start": 34, "end": 40, "text": "a week", "label": "Duration"}, {"start": 124, "end": 133, "text": "last year", "label": "Duration"}, {"start": 89, "end": 96, "text": "nightly", "label": "Frequency"}]}
{"id": 5, "text": "I keep getting headaches and blurred vision in the morning. I take Atorvastatin 20mg daily and aspirin 81mg, and I had a stroke in 2020.", "entities": [{"start": 15, "end": 24, "text": "headaches", "label": "Symptom"}, {"start": 29, "end": 43, "text": "blurred vision", "label": "Symptom"}, {"start": 67, "end": 79, "text": "Atorvastatin", "label": "Medication"}, {"start": 95, "end": 102, "text": "aspirin", "label": "Medication"}, {"start": 80, "end": 84, "text": "20mg", "label": "Dosage"}, {"start": 103, "end": 107, "text": "81mg", "label": "Dosage"}, {"start": 121, "end": 127, "text": "stroke", "label": "Medical History"}, {"start": 85, "end": 90, "text": "daily", "label": "Frequency"}, {"start": 44, "end": 58, "text": "in the morning", "label": "Frequency"}]}
